{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832430/extras/FLAGS.png?t=1730313228\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">An Incredible Geographic Journey!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a simple word-forming game themed around flags and countries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Form words and discover world curiosities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dive into a sea of intriguing information:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover cultures, histories, and surprising facts about the countries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Identify countries through their vibrant flags.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Examine parts of the map and guess which country is hidden behind them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Inspiring Anthems:</strong> Listen to the national anthems of various countries and feel the emotion and patriotism they represent. An immersive experience that connects you with the soul of each nation!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Get ready to explore the planet, broaden your horizons, and connect with the cultural and geographical richness of our fascinating world!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join us and unravel the secrets of the world!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beginner Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2832430/1f596d9b28d4dac88961ede4d1cf41706e144f67.jpg"},{"name":"Curious Traveler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2832430/8b1a50794c7dffbc64541cb81a678b717ec2025d.jpg"},{"name":"World Citizen Adventurer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2832430/0d7827f5535ad5172da658ae03